ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
1 (5 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "Dessert in 10 minutes with vanilla pudding mix, bananas, sour cream and whipped topping."
ins: In large bowl combine sour cream, whipped topping, pudding mix and milk.  Stir well.  In the bottom of a trifle bowl or other glass serving dish, put a layer of cookies, then a layer of pudding mixture, then a layer of bananas.  Repeat until all ingredients are used.  Refrigerate until serving.
